{
  "video_id": "t6eFzt6kFGE",
  "title": "The power of citizen video to create undeniable truths | Yvette Alberdingk Thijm",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12760.0,
      "end_time": 14616.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s 1996"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14640.0,
      "end_time": 16656.0,
      "text": "in Uvira in eastern Congo."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 16680.0,
      "end_time": 18160.0,
      "text": "This is Bukeni."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 18400.0,
      "end_time": 20736.0,
      "text": "Militia commanders walk into his village,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 20760.0,
      "end_time": 22536.0,
      "text": "knock on his neighbors&#39; doors"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 22560.0,
      "end_time": 25720.0,
      "text": "and whisk their children away to training camps."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 26320.0,
      "end_time": 30576.0,
      "text": "Bukeni borrows a video camera from a local wedding photographer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 30600.0,
      "end_time": 32376.0,
      "text": "he disguises as a journalist"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 32400.0,
      "end_time": 35960.0,
      "text": "and he walks into the camps to negotiate the release of the children."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 36560.0,
      "end_time": 40520.0,
      "text": "He filmed footage of the children being trained as soldiers."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 40568.0,
      "end_time": 43158.0,
      "text": "[Soldiers don&#39;t worry!]"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 43202.0,
      "end_time": 44680.0,
      "text": "[You&#39;ll wear uniforms!]"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 45220.0,
      "end_time": 46890.0,
      "text": "[You&#39;ll have free cars!]"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 46920.0,
      "end_time": 47660.0,
      "text": "[Free beans!]"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 47680.0,
      "end_time": 51216.0,
      "text": "Many of these children are under 15 years old,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 51240.0,
      "end_time": 53210.0,
      "text": "and that is a war crime."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 53270.0,
      "end_time": 54410.0,
      "text": "[Free!]"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 55280.0,
      "end_time": 59400.0,
      "text": "But you don&#39;t have to go to eastern Congo to find human rights abuses."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 59760.0,
      "end_time": 63536.0,
      "text": "In America, a country with a rapidly aging population,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 63560.0,
      "end_time": 67936.0,
      "text": "experts estimate that one in 10 people over 60"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 67960.0,
      "end_time": 69960.0,
      "text": "will experience abuse."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 70640.0,
      "end_time": 72976.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a hidden epidemic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 73000.0,
      "end_time": 75776.0,
      "text": "and most of that abuse actually happens at the hands"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 75800.0,
      "end_time": 77880.0,
      "text": "of close caretakers or family."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 79200.0,
      "end_time": 80536.0,
      "text": "This is Vicky."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 80560.0,
      "end_time": 85160.0,
      "text": "Vicky put an iron gate on her bedroom door"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 85400.0,
      "end_time": 88136.0,
      "text": "and she became a prisoner, in fact, in her own house,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 88160.0,
      "end_time": 92520.0,
      "text": "out of fear for her nephew who had taken over her home as a drug den."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 93760.0,
      "end_time": 95560.0,
      "text": "And this is Mary."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 95800.0,
      "end_time": 98216.0,
      "text": "Mary picked up a video camera for the first time in her life"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 98240.0,
      "end_time": 100175.0,
      "text": "when she was 65 years old,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 100200.0,
      "end_time": 104616.0,
      "text": "and she asked Vicky and 99 other older people"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 104640.0,
      "end_time": 108240.0,
      "text": "who had experienced abuse to tell their stories on camera."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 110160.0,
      "end_time": 112150.0,
      "text": "And I am Dutch,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 112400.0,
      "end_time": 115160.0,
      "text": "so in the Netherlands we are obsessed with the truth."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 115400.0,
      "end_time": 117496.0,
      "text": "Now, when you are a child, that&#39;s a great thing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 117520.0,
      "end_time": 120136.0,
      "text": "because you can basically get away with anything,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 120160.0,
      "end_time": 123456.0,
      "text": "like \"Yes, Mama, it was me who smoked the cigars.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 123480.0,
      "end_time": 125120.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 125920.0,
      "end_time": 129896.0,
      "text": "But I think this is why I have dedicated my life"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 129919.00000000001,
      "end_time": 134176.0,
      "text": "to promoting citizen video to expose human rights violations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 134200.0,
      "end_time": 138519.0,
      "text": "because I believe in the power of video to create undeniable truths."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 139400.0,
      "end_time": 141960.0,
      "text": "And my organization, WITNESS,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 141120.0,
      "end_time": 143856.0,
      "text": "helped use the Congolese videos"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 143880.0,
      "end_time": 150359.0,
      "text": "to help convict and send a notorious warlord called Thomas Lubanga to jail."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 151440.0,
      "end_time": 153896.0,
      "text": "And the videos that Mary shot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 153920.0,
      "end_time": 156896.0,
      "text": "we trained Mary and many other elder justice advocates,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 156920.0,
      "end_time": 159736.0,
      "text": "to make sure that the stories of elder abuse"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 159760.0,
      "end_time": 161376.0,
      "text": "reached lawmakers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 161400.0,
      "end_time": 165256.0,
      "text": "and those stories helped convince lawmakers"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 165280.0,
      "end_time": 168440.0,
      "text": "to pass landmark legislation to protect older Americans."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 170280.0,
      "end_time": 172216.0,
      "text": "So I wonder,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 172240.0,
      "end_time": 176896.0,
      "text": "billions of us now have this powerful tool right at our fingertips."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 176920.0,
      "end_time": 178416.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a camera."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 178440.0,
      "end_time": 183256.0,
      "text": "So why are all of us not a more powerful army of civic witnesses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 183280.0,
      "end_time": 185336.0,
      "text": "like Mary and Bukeni?"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 185360.0,
      "end_time": 188216.0,
      "text": "Why is it that so much more video"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 188240.0,
      "end_time": 191760.0,
      "text": "is not leading to more rights and more justice?"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 193000.0,
      "end_time": 197536.0,
      "text": "And I think it is because being an eyewitness is hard."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 197560.0,
      "end_time": 200160.0,
      "text": "Your story will get denied,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 200400.0,
      "end_time": 202896.0,
      "text": "your video will get lost in a sea of images,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 202920.0,
      "end_time": 206600.0,
      "text": "your story will not be trusted, and you will be targeted."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 207920.0,
      "end_time": 209920.0,
      "text": "So how do we help witnesses?"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 211560.0,
      "end_time": 213256.0,
      "text": "In Oaxaca, in Mexico,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 213280.0,
      "end_time": 215856.0,
      "text": "the teachers&#39; movement organized a protest"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 215880.0,
      "end_time": 219400.0,
      "text": "after the president pushed down very undemocratic reforms."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 220160.0,
      "end_time": 223960.0,
      "text": "The federal police came down in buses and started shooting at the protesters."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 224640.0,
      "end_time": 228256.0,
      "text": "At least seven people died and many, many more were wounded."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 228280.0,
      "end_time": 231656.0,
      "text": "Images started circulating of the shootings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 231680.0,
      "end_time": 234960.0,
      "text": "and the Mexican government did what it always does."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 234120.0,
      "end_time": 235536.0,
      "text": "It issued a formal statement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 235560.0,
      "end_time": 238936.0,
      "text": "and the statement basically accused the independent media"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 238960.0,
      "end_time": 241160.0,
      "text": "of creating fake news."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 241400.0,
      "end_time": 242816.0,
      "text": "It said, \"We were not there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 242840.0,
      "end_time": 245576.0,
      "text": "that was not us doing the shooting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 245600.0,
      "end_time": 246960.0,
      "text": "this did not happen.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 248760.0,
      "end_time": 251976.0,
      "text": "But we had just trained activists in Mexico"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 252000.0,
      "end_time": 255776.0,
      "text": "to use metadata strategically with their images."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 255800.0,
      "end_time": 259536.0,
      "text": "Now, metadata is the kind of information that your camera captures"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 259560.0,
      "end_time": 262576.0,
      "text": "that shows the date, the location,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 262600.0,
      "end_time": 264336.0,
      "text": "the temperature, the weather."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 264360.0,
      "end_time": 267776.0,
      "text": "It can even show the very unique way you hold your camera"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 267800.0,
      "end_time": 269536.0,
      "text": "when you capture something."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 269560.0,
      "end_time": 271656.0,
      "text": "So the images started recirculating,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 271680.0,
      "end_time": 274776.0,
      "text": "and this time with the very verifying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 274800.0,
      "end_time": 276880.0,
      "text": "validating information on top of them."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 277960.0,
      "end_time": 280680.0,
      "text": "And the federal government had to retract their statement."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 281520.0,
      "end_time": 285960.0,
      "text": "Now, justice for the people for Oaxaca"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 285120.0,
      "end_time": 286536.0,
      "text": "is still far off,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 286560.0,
      "end_time": 290400.0,
      "text": "but their stories, their truths, can no longer be denied."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 291240.0,
      "end_time": 293160.0,
      "text": "So we started thinking:"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 293400.0,
      "end_time": 294736.0,
      "text": "What if you had \"Proof Mode?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 294760.0,
      "end_time": 296896.0,
      "text": "What if everybody had a camera in their hands"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 296920.0,
      "end_time": 300416.0,
      "text": "and all the platforms had that kind of validating ability."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 300440.0,
      "end_time": 301695.0,
      "text": "So we developed --"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 301720.0,
      "end_time": 306176.0,
      "text": "together with amazing Android developers called the Guardian Project,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 306200.0,
      "end_time": 309496.0,
      "text": "we developed something called a technology that&#39;s called Proof Mode,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 309520.0,
      "end_time": 312695.0,
      "text": "that marries those metadata together with your image,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 312720.0,
      "end_time": 315440.0,
      "text": "and it validates and it verifies your video."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 316520.0,
      "end_time": 320536.0,
      "text": "Now, imagine there is a deluge of images"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 320560.0,
      "end_time": 322960.0,
      "text": "coming from the world&#39;s camera phones."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 323640.0,
      "end_time": 327640.0,
      "text": "Imagine if that information could be trusted just a little bit more,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 328520.0,
      "end_time": 330856.0,
      "text": "what the potential would be for journalists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 330880.0,
      "end_time": 332695.0,
      "text": "for human rights investigators,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 332720.0,
      "end_time": 334160.0,
      "text": "for human rights lawyers."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 335440.0,
      "end_time": 339160.0,
      "text": "So we started sharing Proof Mode with our partners in Brazil"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 339400.0,
      "end_time": 342320.0,
      "text": "who are an amazing media collective called Coletivo Papo Reto."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 344280.0,
      "end_time": 347119.0,
      "text": "Brazil is a tough place for human rights."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 347680.0,
      "end_time": 351640.0,
      "text": "The Brazilian police kills thousands of people every year."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 352400.0,
      "end_time": 354719.0,
      "text": "The only time that there&#39;s an investigation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 355920.0,
      "end_time": 357120.0,
      "text": "guess when?"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 357440.0,
      "end_time": 358640.0,
      "text": "When there&#39;s video."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 360240.0,
      "end_time": 363680.0,
      "text": "Seventeen-year-old Eduardo was killed in broad daylight"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 364640.0,
      "end_time": 366216.0,
      "text": "by the Rio police,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 366240.0,
      "end_time": 368520.0,
      "text": "and look what happens after they kill him."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 370320.0,
      "end_time": 372320.0,
      "text": "They put a gun in the dead boy&#39;s hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 372880.0,
      "end_time": 374600.0,
      "text": "they shoot the gun twice --"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 375840.0,
      "end_time": 377390.0,
      "text": "(Shot)"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 377600.0,
      "end_time": 381720.0,
      "text": "to fabricate their story of self-defense."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 382440.0,
      "end_time": 385896.0,
      "text": "The woman who filmed this was a very, very courageous eyewitness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 385920.0,
      "end_time": 389296.0,
      "text": "and she had to go into hiding after she posted her video"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 389320.0,
      "end_time": 390599.0,
      "text": "for fear of her life."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 391240.0,
      "end_time": 394696.0,
      "text": "But people are filming, and they&#39;re not going to stop filming,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 394720.0,
      "end_time": 397736.0,
      "text": "so we&#39;re now working together with media collectives"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 397760.0,
      "end_time": 400256.0,
      "text": "so the residents on their WhatsApp"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 400280.0,
      "end_time": 403150.0,
      "text": "frequently get guidance and tips,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 403400.0,
      "end_time": 404776.0,
      "text": "how to film safely,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 404800.0,
      "end_time": 407736.0,
      "text": "how to upload the video that you shoot safely,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 407760.0,
      "end_time": 411560.0,
      "text": "how to capture a scene so that it can actually count as evidence."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 412360.0,
      "end_time": 414456.0,
      "text": "And here is an inspiration"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 414480.0,
      "end_time": 417320.0,
      "text": "from a group called MÃ­dia Ninja in Brazil."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 418480.0,
      "end_time": 422320.0,
      "text": "The man on left is a heavily armed military policeman."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 424000.0,
      "end_time": 425496.0,
      "text": "He walks up to a protester --"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 425520.0,
      "end_time": 428736.0,
      "text": "when you protest in Brazil, you can be arrested or worse --"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 428760.0,
      "end_time": 431336.0,
      "text": "and he says to the protester, \"Watch me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 431360.0,
      "end_time": 433880.0,
      "text": "I am going to search you right now.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 435800.0,
      "end_time": 438400.0,
      "text": "And the protester is a live-streaming activist --"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 438840.0,
      "end_time": 440296.0,
      "text": "he wears a little camera --"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 440320.0,
      "end_time": 444256.0,
      "text": "and he says to the military policeman, he says, \"I am watching you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 444280.0,
      "end_time": 447359.0,
      "text": "and there are 5,000 people watching you with me.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 448400.0,
      "end_time": 450856.0,
      "text": "Now, the tables are turned."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 450880.0,
      "end_time": 454159.0,
      "text": "The distant witnesses, the watching audience, they matter."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 455240.0,
      "end_time": 456896.0,
      "text": "So we started thinking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 456920.0,
      "end_time": 459496.0,
      "text": "what if you could tap into that power,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 459520.0,
      "end_time": 461695.0,
      "text": "the power of distant witnesses?"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 461720.0,
      "end_time": 464456.0,
      "text": "What if you could pull in their expertise, their leverage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 464480.0,
      "end_time": 466616.0,
      "text": "their solidarity, their skills"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 466640.0,
      "end_time": 469680.0,
      "text": "when a frontline community needs them to be there?"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 470960.0,
      "end_time": 476296.0,
      "text": "And we started developing a project that&#39;s called Mobilize Us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 476320.0,
      "end_time": 479536.0,
      "text": "because many of us, I would assume,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 479560.0,
      "end_time": 481216.0,
      "text": "want to help"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 481240.0,
      "end_time": 483856.0,
      "text": "and lend our skills and our expertise,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 483880.0,
      "end_time": 486736.0,
      "text": "but we are often not there when a frontline community"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 486760.0,
      "end_time": 489520.0,
      "text": "or a single individual faces an abuse."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 490760.0,
      "end_time": 494416.0,
      "text": "And it could be as simple as this little app that we created"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 494440.0,
      "end_time": 497496.0,
      "text": "that just shows the perpetrator on the other side of the phone"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 497520.0,
      "end_time": 499840.0,
      "text": "how many people are watching him."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 500880.0,
      "end_time": 505216.0,
      "text": "But now, imagine that you could put a layer of computer task routing"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 505240.0,
      "end_time": 506656.0,
      "text": "on top of that."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 506680.0,
      "end_time": 510720.0,
      "text": "Imagine that you&#39;re a community facing an immigration raid,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 511520.0,
      "end_time": 515256.0,
      "text": "and at that very moment, at that right moment, via livestream,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 515280.0,
      "end_time": 517760.0,
      "text": "you could pull in a hundred legal observers."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 518400.0,
      "end_time": 520319.0,
      "text": "How would that change the situation?"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 521320.00000000006,
      "end_time": 525150.0,
      "text": "So we started piloting this with our partner communities in Brazil."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 525390.0,
      "end_time": 527175.0,
      "text": "This is a woman called Camilla,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 527200.0,
      "end_time": 531000.0,
      "text": "and she was able -- she&#39;s the leader in a favela called Favela Skol --"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 531919.0,
      "end_time": 536550.0,
      "text": "she was able to pull in distant witnesses"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 536800.0,
      "end_time": 538136.0,
      "text": "via livestream"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 538160.0,
      "end_time": 539896.0,
      "text": "to help translation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 539920.0,
      "end_time": 541536.0,
      "text": "to help distribution,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 541560.0,
      "end_time": 544335.0,
      "text": "to help amplify her story"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 544360.0,
      "end_time": 547560.0,
      "text": "after her community was forcibly evicted"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 547800.0,
      "end_time": 550960.0,
      "text": "to make room for a very glossy Olympic event last summer."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 552920.0,
      "end_time": 554959.0,
      "text": "So we&#39;re talking about good witnessing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 555920.0,
      "end_time": 559960.0,
      "text": "but what happens if the perpetrators are filming?"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 559120.0,
      "end_time": 562480.0,
      "text": "What happens if a bystander films and doesn&#39;t do anything?"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 563680.0,
      "end_time": 565896.0,
      "text": "This is the story of Chrissy."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 565920.0,
      "end_time": 568256.0,
      "text": "Chrissy is a transgender woman"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 568280.0,
      "end_time": 570896.0,
      "text": "who walked into a McDonald&#39;s in Maryland"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 570920.0,
      "end_time": 572360.0,
      "text": "to use the women&#39;s bathroom."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 572960.0,
      "end_time": 578376.0,
      "text": "Two teens viciously beat her for using that woman&#39;s bathroom,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 578400.0,
      "end_time": 581520.0,
      "text": "and the McDonald&#39;s employee filmed this on his mobile phone."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 582760.0,
      "end_time": 584200.0,
      "text": "And he posted his video,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 584920.0,
      "end_time": 586616.0,
      "text": "and it has garnered"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 586640.0,
      "end_time": 590480.0,
      "text": "thousands of racist and transphobic comments."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 592920.0,
      "end_time": 595800.0,
      "text": "So we started a project that&#39;s called Capturing Hate."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 596840.0,
      "end_time": 600776.0,
      "text": "We took a very, very small sample of eyewitness videos"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 600800.0,
      "end_time": 606175.0,
      "text": "that showed abuse against transgender and gender-nonconforming people."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 606200.0,
      "end_time": 610200.0,
      "text": "We searched two words, \"tranny fight\" and \"stud fight.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 611240.0,
      "end_time": 616296.0,
      "text": "And those 329 videos were watched and are still being watched"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 616320.0,
      "end_time": 618616.0,
      "text": "as we sit here in this theater,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 618640.0,
      "end_time": 622175.0,
      "text": "a stunning almost 90 million times,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 622200.0,
      "end_time": 625416.0,
      "text": "and there are hundreds of thousands of comments with these videos,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 625440.0,
      "end_time": 628320.0,
      "text": "egging on to more violence and more hate."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 630240.0,
      "end_time": 632656.0,
      "text": "So we started developing a methodology"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 632680.0,
      "end_time": 636976.0,
      "text": "that took all that unquantified visual evidence"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 637000.0,
      "end_time": 641416.0,
      "text": "and turned it into data, turning video into data,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 641440.0,
      "end_time": 642696.0,
      "text": "and with that tool,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 642720.0,
      "end_time": 647136.0,
      "text": "LGBT organizations are now using that data"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 647160.0,
      "end_time": 648719.0,
      "text": "to fight for rights."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 649400.0,
      "end_time": 652616.0,
      "text": "And we take that data and we take it back to Silicon Valley,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 652640.0,
      "end_time": 654136.0,
      "text": "and we say to them:"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 654160.0,
      "end_time": 655760.0,
      "text": "\"How is it possible"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 656600.0,
      "end_time": 660576.0,
      "text": "that these videos are still out there"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 660600.0,
      "end_time": 662496.0,
      "text": "in a climate of hate"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 662520.0,
      "end_time": 664376.0,
      "text": "egging on more hate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 664400.0,
      "end_time": 666415.0,
      "text": "summoning more violence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 666440.0,
      "end_time": 668856.0,
      "text": "when you have policies that actually say"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 668880.0,
      "end_time": 672960.0,
      "text": "you do not allow this kind of content? --"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 672120.0,
      "end_time": 674640.0,
      "text": "urging them to change their policies."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 676480.0,
      "end_time": 679136.0,
      "text": "So I have hope."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 679160.0,
      "end_time": 683560.0,
      "text": "I have hope that we can turn more video into more rights and more justice."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 684360.0,
      "end_time": 689640.0,
      "text": "Ten billion video views on Snapchat,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 690760.0,
      "end_time": 692295.0,
      "text": "per day."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 692320.0,
      "end_time": 695616.0,
      "text": "So what if we could turn that Snapchat generation"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 695640.0,
      "end_time": 698856.0,
      "text": "into effective and safe civic witnesses?"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 698880.0,
      "end_time": 702520.0,
      "text": "What if they could become the Bukenis of this new generation?"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 704920.0,
      "end_time": 708935.0,
      "text": "In India, women have already started using Snapchat filters"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 708960.0,
      "end_time": 712840.0,
      "text": "to protect their identity when they speak out about domestic violence."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 712860.0,
      "end_time": 715800.0,
      "text": "[They tortured me at home and never let me go out.]"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 715840.0,
      "end_time": 719416.0,
      "text": "The truth is, the real truth, the truth that doesn&#39;t fit into any TED Talk,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 719440.0,
      "end_time": 722296.0,
      "text": "is fighting human rights abuse is hard."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 722320.0,
      "end_time": 725376.0,
      "text": "There are no easy solutions for human rights abuse."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 725400.0,
      "end_time": 728136.0,
      "text": "And there&#39;s not a single piece of technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 728160.0,
      "end_time": 730400.0,
      "text": "that can ever stop the perpetrators."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 731400.0,
      "end_time": 732840.0,
      "text": "But for the survivors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 733920.0,
      "end_time": 735536.0,
      "text": "for the victims,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 735560.0,
      "end_time": 737359.0,
      "text": "for the marginalized communities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 738160.0,
      "end_time": 742616.0,
      "text": "their stories, their truths, matter."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 742640.0,
      "end_time": 745456.0,
      "text": "And that is where justice begins."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 745480.0,
      "end_time": 746696.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 746720.0,
      "end_time": 749640.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}